<h1 class="title">SEARCH <span>ARTIST</span></h1>
<div class="search-flex">
    <img class='landing-img'
        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1483412033650-1015ddeb83d1?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1773&q=80"
        alt="records photo">
    <div>
        {{!-- We use forms to get the users input and save it as a key value objetc under wahatver name we specify on
        the <input />. Action and methos specified will pass this info to /artist-search as req.query --}}
        <form action="/artist-search" method="GET">
            <label for='artist'></label>
            <input id="searchStyle" type="text" name="artist">
            <button class='button' type="submit">Search</button>
        </form>
        <h2>
            This is the worlds largest album collection. Type in your favorite artist and discover their complete
            discography
        </h2>
    </div>
</div>

{{!-- Basically the form input will actr as an object with key values. The keys are specified as a attribute under name
and the value whatver the user inputs --}}